                                 Zee
                                 ----

Zee an experimental editor and programming environment based on the
Emacs clone Zee (zee.sourceforge.net).

Zee is written in ISO C using POSIX APIs; its only external
dependency is a terminal library, either termcap, Allegro or epocemx.

Zee is free software, licensed under the GNU GPL.

See INSTALL for installation instructions (on EPOC, just install the
SIS file).

Zee is hosted on SourceForge at http://zee.sourceforge.net/

Any questions, comments, or bug reports should be sent to rrt@sc3d.org.
